                <b>Code Files</b><br />
                <p>
                    Code files are stored in systematic way in the directory structure. Care is taken 
                    so that no javascript related code is present on web page and stored in separate project folder in .js file
                    in javascript folder. In similar way all css code is placed in .css files which are stored in project folder
                    under css folder and no css related code is present in aspx file.<br /><br />
                    All project specific files are stored as - <br />

                    1. All .css files related to this project are stored in css/project folder<br />
                    2. All images related to projects are stored at images/project folder<br />
                    3. All javascripts related to projects are stored at javascript/project folder<br />
                    4. All web pages of the projects are stored at project/ folder<br />
                    5. Documentation of the project is stored at project/documentation folder<br />
